This repository contains documentation, helper scripts, and patches for the GPL-licensed patjak/facetimehd Linux driver.

The patch files are intended to be used with the upstream facetimehd driver and should be treated as GPL-2.0-only unless the upstream project states otherwise.

Documentation in this repository may be used under CC0-1.0.

No Apple firmware, calibration files, or other proprietary Apple binaries are included or licensed by this repository.
